## Example 24.4



```python
proc iml;
n=20;
X=4;
estimated_p = X/n;
estimated_q = 1-estimated_p;
variance_of_p = round(estimated_p * estimated_q/(n-1), 0.000001);

sample = repeat(1,4) // repeat(0, 16);
n=nrow(sample);
sum_X = sum(sample);
sum_X_sqr = sample`*sample;
variance = round((sum_X_sqr - sum_X**2/n) / (n-1), 0.000001);
variance_sample_mean = round(variance / n, 0.000001);
std_est_p = round(variance_sample_mean **0.5, 0.001);


print estimated_p estimated_q variance_of_p;
print n sum_X sum_X_sqr variance variance_sample_mean std_est_p;
run;quit;
```

```python
PROC IMPORT
	DATAFILE="C:\Biostat\Exam 24.10.sav"
	DBMS=sav
	OUT=ex24_10
	REPLACE;
RUN;

data ex24_10_diff;
set ex24_10;
diff = Hindleg-Foreleg;
if diff >0 then sign = "+";
else sign="-";
run;
proc print data=ex24_10_diff;
run;
proc iml;
X = {0, 1, 2, 8, 9, 10};
prob = PDF ('BINOMIAL', X, 0.5, 10);
p_value = sum(prob);
print X prob;
print p_value;
run;quit;
```

## Example 24.14



```python
data ex24_14;
input state $ count @@;
cards;
A 65
B 85
;run;
proc freq data=ex24_14;
tables state / nocum norow binomial(all) alpha=0.05;
weight count;
*exact binomial;
run;
```

```python
PROC IMPORT
	DATAFILE="C:\Biostat\Exam 23.1.sav"
	DBMS=sav
	OUT=e_17
	REPLACE;
RUN;

ods graphics off; ods exclude all; ods noresults;
PROC FREQ DATA=e_17;
	weight count;
	tables sex*haircolor / chisq;
		ods output ChiSq=ChiSq_17;
RUN;
ods graphics on; ods exclude none; ods results;

proc print data=ChiSq_17; run;
```

```python
proc iml;
   %macro e_18(x1,x2);
   x={32, 43, 16, 9};
   n={87, 108, 80, 25};
	p={0.200, 0.360, 0.368, 0.398};
	p_t_x1=1/2*(arsin(sqrt(x[&x1]/(n[&x1]+1))) + arsin(sqrt((x[&x1]+1)/(n[&x1]+1))));
	p_t_x2=1/2*(arsin(sqrt(x[&x2]/(n[&x2]+1))) + arsin(sqrt((x[&x2]+1)/(n[&x2]+1))));
	p_ta_x1=round(p_t_x1*180/ CONSTANT('PI'), 0.01);
	p_ta_x2=round(p_t_x2*180/ CONSTANT('PI'), 0.01);
	diff=p_ta_x1-p_ta_x2;
	se=round(sqrt((410.35/(n[&x1]+0.5))+(410.35/(n[&x2]+0.5))), 0.01);
	q=round((p_ta_x1-p_ta_x2)/se, 0.01);
      if q>=3.633 then conclusion='Reject H0' ; 
      else if q <3.633 then conclusion='Do not reject H0' ; 
   print  diff se q conclusion;
%mend ; 
%e_18 (2,3) ; 
%e_18 (2,4) ; 
%e_18 (1,3) ; 
quit;
```

```python
PROC IMPORT
	DATAFILE="C:\Biostat\Exam 24.19.sav"
	DBMS=sav
	OUT=e_19
	REPLACE;
RUN;

PROC FORMAT;
	value condition 1="present" 2="absent";
	value age 1="young" 2="medium" 3="older";
RUN;

ods graphics off; ods exclude all; ods noresults;
PROC freq data=e_19;
	weight count;
	tables condition*ageclass/ chisq trend nocol nopercent;
	ods output ChiSq=ChiSq
					 TrendTest=TrendTest;
run;
ods graphics on; ods exclude none; ods results;

proc print data=ChiSq; run;
```

```python
/* ** TABLE_A ** */
PROC IMPORT
	DATAFILE="C:\Biostat\Exam 24.20.sav"
	DBMS=sav
	OUT=e_20
	REPLACE;
RUN;

PROC FORMAT;
	value species 1="Species_1" 2="Species_2";
	value resisted 1="Resisted" 2="Yielded";
run;

ods graphics off; ods exclude all; ods noresults;
PROC FREQ data=e_20;
	weight count;
	TABLES species*resisted / chisq expected norow nocol nopercent;
	ods output FishersExact=fisher;
run;

DATA e_20a;
	INPUT species resisted count @@;
	CARDS;
	1 1 13 2 1 6 1 2 1 2 2 10
	;
run;

PROC FREQ data=e_20a;
	weight count;
	TABLES species*resisted / chisq expected norow nocol nopercent;
	ods output FishersExact=fisher_a;
run;


/* ** TABLE_B ** */
DATA e_20b;
	INPUT species resisted count @@;
	CARDS;
	1 1 14 2 1 5 1 2 0 2 2 11
	;
run;

PROC FREQ data=e_20b;
	weight count;
	TABLES species*resisted / chisq expected norow nocol nopercent;
	ods output FishersExact=fisher_b;
run;
ods graphics on; ods exclude none; ods results;

proc print data=fisher(firstobs=5 obs=5); run;
```

```python
	;

DATA e_21c;
	input species resisted count @@;
	cards;
	1 1 5 2 1 14 1 2 9 2 2 2
	;
RUN;

DATA e_21d;
	input species resisted count @@;
	cards;
	1 1 6 2 1 13 1 2 8 2 2 3
	;
RUN;

%macro e21 (A,B);
proc freq data=&A;
	tables species*resisted / chisq expected norow nocol nopercent;
	weight count;;
	ods output FishersExact=&B;
run;
%mend;

ods graphics off; ods exclude all; ods noresults;
%e21(e_21a, fisher_a)
%e21(e_21b, fisher_b)
%e21(e_21c, fisher_c)
%e21(e_21d, fisher_d)
ods graphics on; ods exclude none; ods results;

proc print data=fisher_a (firstobs=5 obs=5); run;
```

```python
PROC IMPORT
	DATAFILE="C:\Biostat\Exam 24.22.sav"
	DBMS=sav
	OUT=e_22
	REPLACE;
RUN;

ods graphics off; ods exclude all; ods noresults;
PROC FREQ data=e_22;
	tables row*column / norow nocol nopercent exact binomial;
	weight count;
	ods output FishersExact=Fisher_22;
run; 
ods graphics on; ods exclude none; ods results;

proc print data=Fisher_22 (firstobs=3 obs=6); run;
```

```python
   power = .9;
run;
```

```python
PROC IMPORT
	DATAFILE="C:\Biostat\Exam 24.26.sav"
	DBMS=sav
	OUT=e_26
	REPLACE;
RUN;

PROC FORMAT;
	value mans 1="Protestant" 2="Catholic" 3="Jewish";;
	value fathers 1="Protestant" 2="Catholic" 3="Jewish";
run;

ods graphics off; ods exclude all; ods noresults;
PROC FREQ DATA=e_26;
	tables row*column / agree norow nocol nopercent;
	weight count;
	exact mcnemar;
	ods output SymmetryTest=SymmetryTest;
run; 
ods graphics on; ods exclude none; ods results;

proc print data=SymmetryTest; run;
```

## Example 24.27_약물효과



```python
DATA e_27;
	input mediction application count @@;
	cards;
	1 1 14 2 1 6 1 2 4 2 2 12
	;
run;

proc format;
	value mediction 1="1st" 2="2nd";
	value application 1="A then B" 2="B then A";
run;

ods graphics off; ods exclude all; ods noresults;
proc freq data=e_27;
	tables mediction*application / chisq norow nocol nopercent ;
	weight count;
	ods output ChiSq=chi_27;
run;
ods graphics on; ods exclude none; ods results;

proc print data=chi_27(firstobs=1 obs=1); run;
```

## Example 24.27_복용순서효과



```python
DATA e_27_b;
	input response_b application_b count @@;
	cards;
	1 1 14 2 1 12 1 2 4 2 2 6
	;
run;

proc format;
	value response_b 1="1st" 2="2nd";
	value application_b 1="A then B" 2="B then A";
run;

ods graphics off; ods exclude all; ods noresults;
proc freq data=e_27_b;
	tables response_b*application_b / chisq norow nocol nopercent ;
	weight count;
	ods output ChiSq=chi_27b;
run;
ods graphics on; ods exclude none; ods results;

proc print data=chi_27b(firstobs=1 obs=1); run;
```
